<br><br>
Here's a list of all the new hosts available for your visit to <%= @visit.city %>:

<% @host_data.each do |listing| %>
  <%= listing.host.first_name %> signed up as a host <%= @hosting.distance_from(@visit).round(1) %> mi. from <%= @visit.city || @visit.zipcode %>.
